summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plats 218E and 219W, pages 2 and 3, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle (86300), to rezone certain property in the Northwest 1/4 of Section 19, Township 26 North, Range 4 East, W.M., and in Block 1, Bentonia Highlands from RD 7200 to RM 1600. (Petition of Anthony Ackerman, C.F. 283471)
